text: Kelly Marie Tran (born January 17, 1989) is an American actress. She began acting in 2011. Most of her roles are in short movies and in television. She became well known for acting in two Star Wars movies in 2017 and 2019. Tran was born in San Diego, California. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from San Diego Category:Living people
